# Edge headers for memoturn.ai static assets — Vite copies public/ into
# dist/client (the Workers assets directory), and Workers Static Assets honors
# this file. These rules only apply to asset responses; SSR HTML responses get
# their headers from src/server.ts (assets are served before the worker runs,
# so they'd otherwise carry no security headers at all).

/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains

# Hashed build assets are content-addressed — cache forever.
/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
